to hang out with Marilyn Monroe.

00:04:42.648 --> 00:04:44.050
Trump plays phone a friend

00:04:44.050 --> 00:04:46.819
with the human embodiment
of a Christmas ham.

00:04:46.819 --> 00:04:51.757
