00:04:51.757 --> 00:04:58.064
[ Cheers and applause ]

00:04:58.064 --> 00:05:00.333
Sean Ham-ity.
So that's how close --

00:05:00.333 --> 00:05:04.036
[ Laughter ]

00:05:04.036 --> 00:05:06.805
That's how --
[ Laughter ]

00:05:06.805 --> 00:05:08.540
That's how close those two are,

00:05:08.540 --> 00:05:10.610
